(35, 'movement_rest', 'any', 'any', null, 'Continue safe active play - running, climbing, ball play, pedalling, and supervised stairs. Secure furniture, TVs, windows/balconies, and stairs; keep loose mats, cords, and small objects out of busy walking routes; and avoid seated wheeled walkers.', 0),
